<para style="p">

  <verse number="1" style="v" />Therefore, my beloved brothers whom I long for, my joy and crown, in this way stand firm in the Lord, beloved friends.</para>

<para style="p">

  <verse number="2" style="v" />I am pleading with Euodia, and I am pleading with Syntyche, be of the same mind in the Lord.

  <verse number="3" style="v" />Indeed, I am entreating you also, my true yokefellow: help these women. For they labored with me in spreading the gospel along with Clement and the rest of my fellow workers, whose names are in the Book of Life.</para>
